{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01CNDVN6SsgxyBukjiettS9Q","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"T2.3 complete and merged. ✅\n\n## Summary\n\nImplemented **POST /api/upload** end-to-end and merged it to `master`.\n\n**Files added:**\n- `src/routes/api/upload/+server.ts` — the endpoint handler\n- `src/lib/server/photos.ts` — persistence/utility layer (`insertPhoto`, `publicUrl`, `sanitizeName`, `toPhotoResponse`, `PhotoResponse` type)\n\n**Behavior (matches the T2.3 contract):**\n- Parses `multipart/form-data { photo: File, name? }`\n- Validates content-type `image/*` and size ≤ 8MB → **400** on failure (also rejects empty/missing file)\n- Generates a server-side key `photos/<uuid>.jpg` — never trusts the client filename\n- `PHOTOS_BUCKET.put` with contentType metadata, then inserts a D1 row (`hidden=0`)\n- Returns **201** `{ id, url, name, createdAt }` with the public R2 URL\n- `name` is sanitized (control chars stripped, trimmed, capped at 80 chars); broadcast deferred to Phase 3\n\n**Process notes:**\n- Branched off `master` since T2.2 was already merged (#2).\n- Bundled the uncommitted prerequisite D1 layer (`db.ts`, `migrations/0001_init.sql`) and the `@cloudflare/workers-types` dep that the endpoint needs to build but weren't yet in master.\n- Validation: `pnpm check` → 0 errors (one pre-existing `node` types warning, unrelated); `pnpm build` succeeded with the endpoint bundled. No test/lint scripts exist yet — integration tests are scoped to T2.5.\n- **PR #3** merged into master (squash, commit `4781669`), 0 recoveries needed.\n\n**Cleanup:** the dispatcher can remove this worktree with `planflow_worktree_remove(taskId: \"T2.3\")` from the repo root (I can't, since I'm inside the in-place checkout)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":131,"cache_creation_input_tokens":384,"cache_read_input_tokens":63231,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_toke